'''-{zh-tw:伊莉莎白;zh-hk:伊利沙伯;zh-cn:伊丽莎白;}-·「貝琪」·德沃斯'''（{{lang-en|Elisabeth "Betsy" DeVos}}；{{bd|1958年|1月8日|}}），本姓'''普林斯'''（{{lang-en|Prince}}），是[[美國|美國]][[密歇根州|密歇根州]]一名政治人物、富豪<ref name=PulliamBailey>Pulliam Bailey, Sarah (November 23, 2016). [https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/acts-of-faith/wp/2016/11/23/betsy-devos-trumps-education-pick-is-a-billionaire-philanthropist-with-deep-ties-to-the-reformed-christian-community/ Betsy DeVos, Trump’s education pick, is a billionaire with deep ties to the Christian Reformed community.] {{Wayback|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/acts-of-faith/wp/2016/11/23/betsy-devos-trumps-education-pick-is-a-billionaire-philanthropist-with-deep-ties-to-the-reformed-christian-community/ |date=20180612144812 }} ''[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]]'' Retrieved: November 24, 2016.</ref>、商人、慈善家和教育活動家，第11任[[美國教育部長|美國教育部長]]。

德沃斯于2021年1月7日因为[[2021年美国国会示威|美国国会示威]]而辞去职务<ref>{{Cite news|title=Betsy DeVos resigns as Education secretary, citing Trump’s role in riot|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/education/education-secretary-devos-resigns/2021/01/07/1a3c967a-5155-11eb-b96e-0e54447b23a1_story.html|newspaper=Washington Post|accessdate=2021-01-08|issn=0190-8286|language=en-US|first=Laura|last=Meckler|archive-date=2021-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110133412/https://www.washingtonpost.com/education/education-secretary-devos-resigns/2021/01/07/1a3c967a-5155-11eb-b96e-0e54447b23a1_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 簡介 ==
她曾擔任許多社會、文化和政治運動和組織的領導，並擔任多年{{le|密歇根州共和黨|Michigan Republican Party}}的主席。她是風追求集團（{{lang|en|Windquest Group}}）、迪克和貝琪·德沃斯家庭基金會（{{lang|en|Dick and Betsy DeVos Family Foundation}}）及美國兒童聯合會（{{lang|en|American Federation for Children}}）的主席；同時也是[[约翰·肯尼迪表演艺术中心|约翰·肯尼迪表演艺术中心]]的德沃斯藝術管理學院（{{lang|en| DeVos Institute for Arts Management}}）董事會成員<ref name="Philanthropy">{{cite journal |author = Philanthropy Staff |date = 2013 |title = Interview with Betsy DeVos, the Reformer |journal = [[Philanthropy_(magazine)|Philanthropy]] |format = print and online |issue = Spring |location = Washington, D.C. |publisher = [[Philanthropy_Roundtable|Philanthropy Roundtable]] |url = http://www.philanthropyroundtable.org/topic/excellence_in_philanthropy/interview_with_betsy_devos |access-date = 2013-07-08 |archive-date = 2013-05-30 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130530160955/http://www.philanthropyroundtable.org/topic/excellence_in_philanthropy/interview_with_betsy_devos |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

德沃斯的丈夫{{tsl|en|Dick DeVos|狄克·戴弗斯}}，為美國多層次傳銷公司[[安麗|安麗]]（Amway）前執行長，其父親為安麗共同創辦人[[理查·狄維士|理查·狄維士]]<ref>Chase Peterson-Withorn (November 23rd 2016),[http://www.forbes.com/sites/chasewithorn/2016/11/23/trump-picks-betsy-devos-daughter-in-law-of-billionaire-amway-cofounder-for-education-secretary/#1e1f29875313 Trump Picks Betsy DeVos, Daughter-In-Law Of Billionaire Amway Cofounder, For Education Secretary] {{Wayback|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/chasewithorn/2016/11/23/trump-picks-betsy-devos-daughter-in-law-of-billionaire-amway-cofounder-for-education-secretary/#1e1f29875313 |date=20170205205754 }} Forbes, Retrieved 20th December 2016.</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=How Betsy DeVos Could Fix America's Broken Education System|date=January 22, 2017|url=http://newhampshirereview.com/education/how-bestsy-devos-fix-education-system/|website=NewHampshireReview.com|publisher=The New Hampshire Review|accessdate=25 January 2017|archive-date=2018-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612163135/https://newhampshirereview.com/education/how-bestsy-devos-fix-education-system/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。德沃斯的弟弟，前美國海軍[[海豹部隊|海豹部隊]]軍官[[艾瑞克·普林斯|艾瑞克·普林斯]]，是美國安全顧問、私人軍事公司[[Academi|美國黑水]]創辦人<ref>{{cite book|last=Scahill|first=Jeremy|title=Blackwater: The Rise of the World's Most Powerful Mercenary Arm|url=https://archive.org/details/blackwaterriseof00scah|publisher=Nation Books|year=2008|asin=B0097CYTYA}}{{cite book|last=Prince|first=Erik|title=Civilian Warriors: The Inside Story of Blackwater and the Unsung Heroes of the War on Terror|url=https://archive.org/details/civilianwarriors0000prin|publisher=Portfolio|year=2014|isbn=978-1-59184-745-8}}</ref>。德沃斯是美國普林斯有限公司（Prince Corporation）創辦人{{tsl|en|Edgar Prince|艾德加·普林斯}}的女兒<ref name="Edgar D. Prince">"[http://www.newnetherlandinstitute.org/history-and-heritage/dutch_americans/edgar-d-prince/ Edgar D. Prince] {{Wayback|url=http://www.newnetherlandinstitute.org/history-and-heritage/dutch_americans/edgar-d-prince/ |date=20190331222427 }}". [[New_Netherland_Institute|New Netherland Institute]]. newnetherlandinstitute.org.</ref><ref>Benjamin Wermund and Kimberly Hefling (November 25th, 2016), [http://www.politico.com/story/2016/11/betsy-devos-education-secretary-civil-rights-gay-transgender-students-231837 Trump’s education secretary pick supported anti-gay causes] {{Wayback|url=http://www.politico.com/story/2016/11/betsy-devos-education-secretary-civil-rights-gay-transgender-students-231837 |date=20171229033220 }}, [[Politico|Politico]], Retrieved 14 December 2016.</ref>。

2016年11月23日，[[美國總統|美國總統]][[唐納·川普|唐納·川普]]提名德沃斯出任[[美國教育部長|美國教育部長]]<ref name="BuzzfeedDeVos">{{cite news | authors=Hensley-Clancy, Molly | date=2016-11-23 | title=Trump Picks Betsy DeVos As Education Secretary | work=[[BuzzFeed|Buzzfeed.com]] | url=https://www.buzzfeed.com/mollyhensleyclancy/trump-announces-betsy-devos-as-education-secretary | access-date=2016-11-23 | archive-date=2016-12-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161202104228/https://www.buzzfeed.com/mollyhensleyclancy/trump-announces-betsy-devos-as-education-secretary | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

美国东部时间2017年2月7日，[[美国参议院|美国参议院]]全体院会对其任命案进行表决，因為兩名共和黨女參議員投反對票，投票结果为50-50，最后副总统兼参议院议长[[迈克·彭斯|迈克·彭斯]]投下了关键的一票，最终使得任命案得到惊险通过。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.voachinese.com/a/trump-education-nominee-20170207/3709875.html |title=副总统投关键票 参院批准德沃斯任教育部长 |publisher=美國之音 |date=2017-02-08 |accessdate=2017-02-09 |archive-date=2017-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170208233058/http://www.voachinese.com/a/trump-education-nominee-20170207/3709875.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>這是首次由副總統參與參議院內閣同意權投票，並行使關鍵一票。

